00:35:19.040 --> 00:35:23.760
[Unknown]: And you have to, I mean, a government has to work in this framework only?

00:35:24.880 --> 00:35:27.840
[Amit Varma]: No, I mean, I think there are certain frameworks along which you think,

00:35:27.840 --> 00:35:32.160
[Amit Varma]: for example, one framework along which I certainly think is a framework of freedom.

00:35:32.160 --> 00:35:36.320
