[Amit Varma]: lower class Muslims around them worthy of their moral consideration. So that answers this question,

00:40:21.760 --> 00:40:28.000
[Amit Varma]: how could you? You could because you don't see this person as human. And that's a very

00:40:28.000 --> 00:40:32.720
[Amit Varma]: disturbing thing. And I think what happens is like the earlier point that you made and that you

00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:38.960
[Amit Varma]: went back to is that technology reinforces, you know, technology helps us form these echo chambers

00:40:38.960 --> 00:40:44.080
[Amit Varma]: where we find like minded people and where we can stay with the in our comfort zones with

00:40:44.080 --> 00:40:49.760
[Amit Varma]: tribes we feel comfortable with. So, you know, will this make us one world or will this actually

