[Unknown]: All right. Okay, let's take some last few questions.

01:08:13.600 --> 01:08:19.680
[Unknown]: Damanbir Singh, whose Twitter handle is DamanbirSingh9 asks for spreading ideas of

01:08:19.680 --> 01:08:25.280
[Unknown]: liberalism, which is better a podcast championing liberalism, criticizing reactionary forces with

