[Unknown]: Vimal's second question was, do you think Dan Bilzerian made all his money playing poker?

01:11:15.120 --> 01:11:19.040
[Amit Varma]: No, of course not. He's just like a celebrity. He's like the Kim Kardashian of that kind of

